OL,3,CPolitician who 'let down' Jersey
OL,4,Cpeople avoids jail despite immigration
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FA Jersey politician has been given 120
OL,8,Fhours of community service for
OL,9,Femploying five Rwandan nationals in
OL,10,Fhis laundry business without the
OL,11,Fcorrect work permits.
OL,13,FPhilip Ozouf was sentenced at Jersey's
OL,14,FRoyal Court today.
OL,16,FThe judge told Ozouf he has "let down
OL,17,Fthe people of Jersey who put their
OL,18,Ftrust in you."
