OL,7,FProsecution Crown Advocate William
OL,8,FRedgrave said although the workers
OL,9,Fwere grateful for the employment, they
OL,10,Fwere only paid around #10-#11 per hour
OL,11,Fat the Savoy Hotel and #12- #12.50 at
OL,12,Fthe launderette, and there was a
OL,13,F'degree of exploitation'.
