OL,7,FUnder Jersey law, Rwandans need a visa
OL,8,Fto work in the island, and if
OL,9,Fapproved, the visa is stamped in their
OL,10,Fpassport. If the Jersey Customs and
OL,11,Fimmigration service extend the visa,
OL,12,Fthe passport is stamped again.
OL,13,FEmployees on a work permit can take on
OL,14,Fextra employment, but it has to be in
OL,15,Fthe same sector. In this case Ozouf
OL,16,Fhad only arranged for these nationals
OL,17,Fto come on a hospitality visa - and
OL,18,Ftherefore they were not allowed to
OL,19,Fwork in his launderette or home.
