OL,7,FThe court heard workers stayed at
OL,8,FOzouf's home in St Saviour in an annex
OL,9,Fand were charged #500-a-month for
OL,10,Frent, which was deducted from their
OL,11,Fwages at the Savoy, and then were paid
OL,12,Fseparately for the work at the
OL,13,Flaunderette.
OL,15,FThey also did work including putting
OL,16,Fup election posters and handing out
OL,17,Fleaflets.
