OL,7,FThe court heard that one of the
OL,8,Fhospitality workers, Liliane
OL,9,FGikundiro, who had a hospitality work
OL,10,Fpermit was expected to do laundry and
OL,11,Fhouse cleaning and other tasks at
OL,12,FOzouf's home when she had a day off
OL,13,Ffrom the laundry.
OL,15,FThe court heard messages were sent to
OL,16,Fher from Ozouf on July 10th 2023
OL,17,Fsaying: "I went upstairs and saw the
OL,18,Fironing isn't done, are you going to
OL,19,Fdo the ironing?"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/14
