OL,3,CPolitician who 'let down' Jersey
OL,4,Cpeople avoids jail despite immigration
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FAnother on 18 July said: "I'd
OL,8,Fappreciate it if you can do a clean up
OL,9,Fof the main house."
OL,11,FIn a victim impact statement she said
OL,12,Fshe felt she wasn't treated well and
OL,13,Fis still owed money.
OL,15,FShe said: "I didn't feel able to
OL,16,Frefuse this work or lack of contract
OL,17,Fdue to dependence on employment."
OL,19,FShe added her mental health
OL,20,Fdeteriorated during her time working
OL,21,Fwith Ozouf.
