OL,4,Cpeople avoids jail despite immigration
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FAlthough she didn't receive full pay
OL,8,Fin the end, she found working for
OL,9,FOzouf ""enjoyable and fun'.
OL,11,FOzouf had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Ffour counts of assisting unlawful
OL,13,Fimmigration and one count of
OL,14,Fattempting to assist unlawful
OL,15,Fimmigration - the offences span from
OL,16,FDecember 2021 to May 2023 and included.
OL,18,FRoberto Lora had previously pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to to one count of attempting
OL,20,Fto assist unlawful immigration.
