OL,4,Cpeople avoids jail despite immigration
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe defence, Advocate Bell, told the
OL,8,Fcourt Ozouf feels genuine remorse for
OL,9,Fhis crimes.
OL,11,FHe told the Royal Court this is about
OL,12,Fillegal working, rather than illegal
OL,13,Fimmigration, and that the case has had
OL,14,Fa personal, professional and financial
OL,15,Fimpact that has left his "political
OL,16,Fcareer in tatters."
OL,18,FLora's defence advocate said his
OL,19,Fremorse in clear and genuine, and has
OL,20,Fa low risk of reoffending.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/14
