OL,4,Cpeople avoids jail despite immigration
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FLora was handed a #5,000 fine.
OL,9,FJersey's Minister for Justice and Home
OL,10,FAffairs, Deputy Mary Le Hegarat, said
OL,11,Fafter the court hearing: "Today's
OL,12,Fsentencing by the Royal Court is a
OL,13,Fpowerful reminder that breaches of
OL,14,FJersey's immigration legislation will
OL,15,Fnot be tolerated."
